Body: to be in partnership with UBER GRAB GOCAR needs additional permit by the government, it took us almost 6months to complete all  1. must have minimum 5cars, but they will said ideally 6 car 2. 1300cc engine on those innitial cars 3. all car must be strictly under companies name 4. the initial cars must be stated on the incorporation assets and tax 5. the incorporation documents must exclusively state code of Classification of Indonesian Business Sector Standard (KBLI) with number 7710 which is Commercial Transport Service 6. must have business license (SIUP) 7. All cars must pass and acquire initial periodic test (Keur / KIR) and be extended+re-test every 6months 8. All the cars will be embossed at the chassis and given testing attendance book 9. All the cars will be given special stickers to differentiate which on is taxi online, and the sticker is permanently stick to the front and back of windshild mirror 10. Must have license of the operator of a special lease car (IPAS) for periode of 5years 11. Must have minimum deposit on the bank account, in which also stated legally on the incorporation paper and notarial deed 12. Must have company tax license 13. Must have company domicile, and initial car pools area, which can accommodate the cars 14. All the cars must have TLO Total-Lost-Only insurance 15. Rental Assignment Letter (surat tugas rental) 16. power of attorney for registration (surat kuasa pendaftaran) 17. Drivers employment contract and mutation (komtrak kerja driver dan mutasi) 18. Must have Car Workshop partnership 19. certification of vehicle type test (Sertifikasi Uji Tipe Kendaraan)  I think this is all

Author: kermitas
Title: ğŸš§[ANN][PreCrowdsale]ğŸš—FRASğŸš•Official UBER partner | Crypto TAXI +Real Use Cases
Body: That is not good news ://.   The FRAS COIN it self will be distributed manually If may I suggest something. Many investors may not invest if coins/tokens that are 'distributed manually'. For example I didn't invest into Fire Lotto because I have checked their smart contracts (as well as luck of them). They will do 'manual distribution' and no one knows if that is true or a scam.  When we are speaking about Ethereum there should be no space for any 'manual actions' to eliminate possibility that - for example - issuer (in this case Frasindo) will be hacked and all coins/tokens or invested funds will be stolen. Luckily that is not a problem on Ethereum to use one of ERC20 smart contracts that will absolutely guaranteed that right number of Fras Coins will belongs to investor (to the Ethereum address from which ETHers were send).  Before crowdsale start (on Ethereum that means 'before hardcoded block number') all investors should be able to review all smart contracts (there can be one or more) that will be used for crowdfunding process and take their own decision to invest or not.
